      "body" : "Please not, that at least on Ubuntu (Unity) the icon is only used for the window decoration, but not for the launcher. To have the icon visible (instead of the ugly question mark), you&#39;d need to specify appropriate <code>.dektop</code> file. See my description <b><a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/36311638/javafx-ubuntu-stage-dock-icon-wont-work/36316722#36316722\">here</a></b>"
