    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Assuming your stage is \"stage\" and the file is on the filesystem:</p>\n\n<pre><code>stage.getIcons().add(new Image(\"file:icon.png\"));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>As per the comment below, if it's wrapped in a containing jar you'll need to use the following approach instead:</p>\n\n<pre><code>stage.getIcons().add(new Image(&lt;yourclassname&gt;.class.getResourceAsStream(\"icon.png\")));\n</code></pre>\n"
