    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Another easy way to insert your own icon on the title bar in JavaFX is to add the image to your primary stage using the following method:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Image ico = new Image(\"resources/images/iconLogo.png\");\nstage.getIcons().add(ico);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Make sure your import javafx.scene.image.Image (if using an ide like netbeans this should be automatically done for you).</p>\n"
