    "body" : "<p>If you have have a images folder and the icon is saved in that use this </p>\n\n<pre><code>stage.getIcons().add(new Image(&lt;yourclassname&gt;.class.getResourceAsStream(\"/images/comparison.png\")));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>and if you are directly using it from your package which is not a good practice use this</p>\n\n<pre><code>stage.getIcons().add(new Image(&lt;yourclassname&gt;.class.getResourceAsStream(\"comparison.png\")));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>and if you have a folder structure and you have your icon inside that use</p>\n\n<pre><code>stage.getIcons().add(new Image(&lt;yourclassname&gt;.class.getResourceAsStream(\"../images/comparison.png\")));\n</code></pre>\n"
